    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my trips. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner today! If you're looking for a dependable, great-looking ride that won't let you down, this is definitely the one. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd be happy to chat more about it!",
